text: Tea Akhvlediani (born 21 January 1975) is a Georgian diplomat politician. She is the current State Minister for Reconciliation and Civic Equality of Georgia since 6 August 2020. She was ambassador of Georgia to Estonia from 2014 to 2019. == Other websites == * Biography on Georgian Goverment website Category:1975 births Category:Politicians from Georgia (country) Category:Living people
